descp2: An optional string from: "NDHWC", "NCDHW". Defaults to "NDHWC". The data format of the input and output data. With the default format "NDHWC", the data is stored in the order of: [batch, in_depth, in_height, in_width, in_channels]. Alternatively, the format could be "NCDHW", the data storage order is: [batch, in_channels, in_depth, in_height, in_width].
